  "title": "ICT Project Manager [ 1 Year Contract | Gov Project ]",
  "description": "<ul><li><strong>Monday to Friday 8:30am to 6pm</strong></li><li><strong>Located at Novena</strong></li><li><strong>1 Year Contract - Renewable </strong></li><li><strong>Gov Project - Defence sector </strong></li></ul><p><strong></strong><br /><strong>Responsibilities</strong></p><ul><li>Project Manager shall be a suitably qualified personnel with experience to interface with the different teams (eg. System Infrastructure team, Security Team and Others).</li><li>Be the POC to present at all Monthly progress meetings, he/she shall report the progress to the Authority.</li><li>Lead an engineering team to review, modify, design and implementation the new and existing system.</li><li>Lead the joint effort between the Authority’s appointed vendors and the engineering team for any troubleshooting failure/faults related to the network implementation on the existing system.</li><li>Highlight any technical or schedule risk regarding the project. He/she shall also present to the Authority mitigation measure with solutions to move the project forward to reduce the impact to the technical and schedule impact.</li></ul><p><br /><strong>Requirements</strong></p><ul><li>Diploma in Computer Science or equivalent</li><li>IT System Management experience of various aspect</li><li>Shall have at least three (3) years of ICT Project Management.</li><li>Familiar with Government policy and process</li></ul><p><br /><em>Applicants who possess relevant experience for the above responsibilities are most welcome to apply. If you do not possess the above experience, your application will still be considered on individual merits and you may be contacted for other opportunities. </em></p><p><em>By submitting your personal data and/or resume, you give consent to collection, use and disclosure of your personal data and/or resume by the company (or its agent) for the purpose of the processing and administration by the company relating to this job application. </em><br /></p><p>**We regret to inform that only shortlisted candidates would be notified</p><p>Interested applicants may send their resume to <a href=\"mailto:apply95@talentvis.com\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"><strong>apply95@talentvis.com</strong></a> or click <strong>APPLY NOW</strong></p><p>Talentvis Singapore Pte Ltd | EA License No: 04C3537<br />EA Personnel Name: Mok Mun Teng (Katrina) | EA Personnel No: R25157733<br /></p>",
